des: Surgeons in 3D Printing is an interview-based show where Dr Ruchi interviews surgeons across the globe who are pioneers and have a rich experience of working with Medical 3D Printing Technology. Here they share their insights and solve problems related to the implementation of 3D Technology for upcoming surgeons in the field.
